<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62346734-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s389d"><num value="389d">§ 389d.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall have power to make such rules and regulations as may be necessary to carry out the provisions of sections 389 to 389e of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id62346735-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1936-06-22/ch692/s5">June 22, 1936, ch. 692, § 5</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/49/1804">49 Stat. 1804</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
